headline: AutoZone to Release Second Quarter Fiscal 2026 Earnings March 3, 2026
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., Feb. 10, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- AutoZone, Inc. (NYSE: AZO), the leading retailer and distributor of automotive replacement parts and accessories in the Americas, will release results for its second quarter ended Saturday, February 14, 2026, before market open on Tuesday, March 3, 2026.
